  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There will be successive changes in traditional Chinese medicine rehabilitation for stroke
      patients with limb hemiparetic through therapy of acupuncture and moxibustion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      There will be difference in stroke outcomes of ischemic stroke patients with limb hemiparetic
      from acute to chronic phase under Lu' acupuncture and moxibustion.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
