    <description>The treatment group：60 patients receive Acupuncture ，selecting acupoint on:Shenting（DU24), Baihui（DU20）, Fengchi（GB20), Hanyan（GB4）, Jianyu（LI15）, Quchi（LI11）,Waiguan（SJ5）, Zusanli（ST36）, Fenglong（ST40）, Xingjian(LV2), Yongquan（KI1）, 20minutes each time，ten times / treatment course，two treatment courses in total.</description>
